snippet.title: Puyo Puyo!! 20th Anniversary SUBBED - Prologue + Ringo
snippet.description:
Ringo somehow ends up in Primp Town after an experiment from Risukuma goes horribly wrong. Confused and lost, Ringo tries to find her friends Maguro and Risukuma, and hopefully find a way home. But potential danger also lurks in the corner...
